lauro f cavazos says its time americans 
start caring about the educational needs of all citizens and 
he is promising to put the focus on the issue if confirmed as the 
next education secretary 
i know this wont be turned around in a decade we cant wait 
any longer weve waited too long cavazos told the senate labor 
and human resources committee as it considered his nomination 
friday to replace outgoing education secretary william j bennett 
if sworn in cavazos would become the first hispanic member of a 
presidents cabinet 
cavazos 61 appeared headed for an easy confirmation with 
senators praising the son of a cattle foreman on the king ranch in 
