the scion of a wealthy indian family 
made aviation history today when he finished a 6000mile journey 
from britain to new delhi in an ultralight aircraft in 23 days 
vijaypat singhania landed in his red and white lesprit dindian 
post to loud applause at new delhis safdarjung airport around noon 
i wanted to be an ambassador for my country and show people 
