carrying a baseball bat prepare to step from the sea for the first 
time to retrieve a baseball sitting on the shore 
in another a rattlesnake with a pointer in its mouth lectures a 
class of other snakes showing them a chart of a mans leg with a 
boot the bare part of the leg is marked ok and the boot is 
marked no good 
