supplies 
diarrhea can kill by robbing the body of critically important 
substances such as sodium potassium and magnesium the fluid loss 
associated with diarrhea can lead to sudden collapse of the blood 
vessels and loss of bicarbonates can turn the bodys internal 
fluids to acid disrupting normal metabolism 
